displayName: Android - deviceManagementType - Android Enterprise or AOSP user
Win - DeviceType - AVD Personal, W365, AVD Pooled
rule: ((device.deviceName -startsWith "avd-pers-") and (device.enrollmentProfileName -eq $null)) or (device.model -contains "Cloud PC") or (device.operatingSystemSKU -eq "ServerRdsh") or ((device.model -eq $null) and (device.enrollmentProfileName -eq $null))
